wdi2-SP.POP.65UP.FE.IN.def: Female population 65 years of age or older. Population is based on the de facto definition of population, which counts all residents regardless of legal status or citizenship.
wdi2-SP.POP.65UP.FE.IN.name: Population ages 65 and above
wdi2-SP.POP.65UP.FE.IN.source: World Bank staff estimates using the World Bank's total population and age/sex distributions of the United Nations Population Division's World Population Prospects: 2019 Revision.
